data.text:
To begin the intake process or learn more about the mental health services Sharp Mesa Vista Mid City offers, please call 619-478-8220 or submit an outpatient treatment request form.

At Sharp Mesa Vista Mid City, we accept most major health insurance plans. Most of our services are either covered in full or in part by insurance. One of our intake professionals will work with your insurance company to ensure that you receive the maximum coverage allowed by your plan.

Your mental health and well-being are our top priority. And we're here to support you every step of the way. We offer a variety of mental health resources to help you and your loved ones stay informed and be empowered to manage your care.
